<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>가입 완료 - 케빈아카데미</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favicon.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="auth-container">
    <div class="auth-card">
      <div class="auth-header">
        <h1>가입이 완료되었습니다!</h1>
        <p>케빈아카데미 첨삭 관리 시스템</p>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0;">
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong><%= name %></strong> 학생, 환영합니다!</p>
        <div style="background: #eef5f1; border: 2px solid #133327; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 1rem 0;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">학생 아이디</p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: bold; color: #133327; letter-spacing: 2px;"><%= studentId %></p>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #888; margin-top: 1rem;">이 아이디로 로그인할 수 있습니다.<br>학부모 연락처와 이메일로도 전송되었습니다.</p>
      </div>

      <a href="/management" class="btn btn-primary btn-full" style="text-decoration: none; text-align: center;">로그인하기</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
